        <p itemprop="text">Yes — GA4 is completely free for all Kenyan businesses, with no usage limits for standard business websites. The paid tier (GA4 360, priced at hundreds of thousands of US dollars annually) is designed for enterprise companies with billions of events per month — Kenyan SMEs have no practical need for it. Google Analytics 4 and Google Search Console together give a Kenyan business all the data needed to make informed decisions about website content, SEO investment, and marketing spend — at zero cost.</p>
